reviewText: My mother and I really enjoyed this soap when it came out on Tv that I've been looking for it until I found it here and bought it,  but you fail to say it's not the entire soap that it's been cut alot that you ruined it.

I gave it 5 stars cause I LOVE this novela bt it really needed 4stars cause it doesn't have the FULL episodes it skips a lot good parts very good ones and that really sucks cause I mean in a DVD should last the full episodes. BT its still an awesome one so happy and disappointed.
This is an excellent telenovela and the ending was outstanding, actually the most unique ending I have ever seen in a telenovela.
I missed this "Telenovela" on TV. So I ordered and I am glad I did. Like it and as soon another of my favorite ones comes along, I will get it too.

Me Gusto Mucho el DVD aunque en algunas partes se notan cortes bruscos en la Edicin. El DVD 1 tiene una Escena repetida. La Historia en gral es muy Dinamica, Entretenida, Tiene Humor, Tiene Drama y Te Mantiene Espectante.
Hubiera preferido que dejaran algunas de las peleas de Hortencia con Manuela y de Manuela con Isabel pero no estan. Pese a todo a mi me gusto, la recomiendo por haber sido una buena Telenovela, por contar con un Buen Elenco y por la Historia en si.

The show was really good. I hope the editing on the DVD does it justice. I am willing to take a chance because I enjoyed the novela so much when it aired. I am thrilled it's coming out on DVD and can't wait until it's released.
